# =============================================================================
# ClawBench Agent Configuration Example — Claude Backend
# ClawBench 智能体配置示例 — Claude 后端
# =============================================================================
#
# This file is NOT loaded (the .yaml.example extension is ignored by LoadAgents).
# 本文件不会被加载（.yaml.example 后缀会被 LoadAgents 忽略）。
# To use, copy as e.g. my-claude-agent.yaml and modify the config.
# 实际使用时请复制为如 my-claude-agent.yaml 并修改配置。
# =============================================================================

id: claude-coder
name: Claude 编码
icon: 🟣
specialty: 复杂编码、架构设计、代码重构
backend: claude
model: claude-sonnet-4-6
system_prompt: |
  You are an expert software engineer specializing in complex coding, architecture design, and code refactoring.
  You write clean, maintainable code and provide thorough explanations of your design decisions.

# command [optional]: Override the default CLI command.
# command: /home/user/claude-local
